ExecDesc.value: PHP CDF File Handling Infinite Loop

EngDesc.value: A denial of service vulnerability has been reported in PHP. It is due to an error in the FileInfo module while handling nelements in the processing of CDF files. A remote attacker can exploit the vulnerability by sending crafted CDF files to a web application running a vulnerable version of PHP. A successful attack will result in an infinite loop, which can cause a denial of service condition.
